commit_message: If no arguments are passed to the script, exit with code 0
Don't compute entropy for ORFs with a single codon
Transcript length, ORF length and HMMER score are no longer log-transformed
Fix a bug in the entropy function
Add a default value for the 'frame_number' parameter
Substitute double quotes by single quotes
Add output_fasta as an argument of the main function
Add an option to save a FASTA file of the predicted proteins
Add descriptions of the features to the README.md
Change channel order in the Conda environment file
Calculate hexamer frequency only in the ORFs
'mopal_make_hexamer_table.py' now accepts a FASTA containing complete protein-coding transcripts
Change the name of the main scripts
Compute the SNR of the ORF, not the whole sequence
Update the XGBoost package version in the environment file
Compute the Fickett score of the ORF, not the whole sequence
Use 'shutil.rmtree' to remove the HMMER directory after parsing the output
Use 'os.path.basename' to get the FASTA file name
Name of the HMMER folder depends on the input FASTA file
Use shutil.rmtree() to remove non-empty directory
Clean the HMMER directory before trying to delete it
Add scikit-learn to the environment file
Add human and mouse hexamer tables
Improve the wording of the 'output_features' argument
